 Here is an example XML file for your mission plan:
```php
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<mission>
    <name>Orchard Exploration</name>
    <description>Exploring the orchard and taking pictures of trees.</description>
    <tasks>
        <task id="1">
            <name>Take a picture of the northern most tree</name>
            <location>[Northern most tree coordinates]</location>
            <action>Take a picture</action>
        </task>
        <task id="2">
            <name>Drive to the middle of the orchard</name>
            <location>[Middle of the orchard coordinates]</location>
            <action>Drive to location</action>
        </task>
        <task id="3">
            <name>Take a picture of two trees next to each other</name>
            <location>[Eastern end middle coordinates]</location>
            <action>Take a picture</action>
        </task>
    </tasks>
</mission>
```
Please replace the `[Northern most tree coordinates]`, `[Middle of the orchard coordinates]`, and `[Eastern end middle coordinates]` with the actual coordinates of the trees you want to take pictures of. 